   1:main.c        **** /*===================================    
   2:main.c        **** Final Design Project: Heart Rate Monitor  
   3:main.c        **** Paige Spencer & Josh Wild    
   4:main.c        **** October 30 2025    
   5:main.c        **** Weeks 1-4:
   6:main.c        **** Write code to successfully measure, filter, and display heart rate.
   7:main.c        **** - Read IR sensor data from MAX30102
   8:main.c        **** - Filter noise (moving average)
   9:main.c        **** - Detect peaks to calculate BPM
  10:main.c        **** - Display BPM on OLED
  11:main.c        **** - Indicate heart rate range with messages:
  12:main.c        ****     * Normal Resting (60–100 BPM)
  13:main.c        ****     * Moderate-Intensity Exercise (100–140 BPM)
  14:main.c        ****     * High Intensity Exercise (>140 BPM)
  15:main.c        **** ========================================*/   
